long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Jumpy Kangaroo is an HTML5 game where players control a kangaroo and must help it jump over obstacles and collect coins.
Jumpy Kangaroo is an exciting and challenging HTML5 game. That will test your reflexes and keep you on the edge of your seat. In this game, you control a kangaroo and must help it jump over obstacles and collect coins.
As you progress through the levels, the obstacles will become more numerous, and the gaps between them will become smaller. Be sure to time your jumps carefully to avoid falling into the water or hitting an obstacle.
In addition to the obstacles, you have coins scattered throughout the levels you can collect to earn points. These coins can be tricky to collect. As they are often placed in difficult-to-reach areas or moving quickly, you'll need to be quick and agile to collect them all.
The simple yet challenging gameplay, combined with the cute and colorful graphics. Make this game a must-play for anyone who loves arcade-style games. So why not try it and see how far you can jump?
